text: Ashley Estes Kavanaugh is an American public official and former political aide. Since 2004, she has been the wife of Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States Brett Kavanaugh. Kavanaugh was born in Abilene, Texas. ==References== Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Texas Category:People from Abilene, Texas Category:1974 births
